<subSubSection id="CE7F19A9B50D182B7C0918F6CFE6A2F7" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="018070E48291321A137DAE789C7620FC" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicName id="2B273A134D76008CC7DBF00D6E2ACB6B" authority="Hull, 1945" authorityName="Hull" authorityYear="1945" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Archimicrodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Archimicrodon" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Archimicrodon</taxonomicName>
Hull, 1945: 75. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="1F58C107B362AD5324A1843CAFBA939F" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Microdon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microdon digitator" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="digitator">Microdon digitator</taxonomicName>
Hull, 1937: 19, by original designation.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CD3157793980C245234E018BA64615A4" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicName id="036ACD4B50DA6EFA5A043C8D09800661" authority="" authorityName="" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Hovamicrodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hovamicrodon" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Hovamicrodon</taxonomicName>
(Subgenus) Keiser, 1971: 248. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="566EC3A563A402A54E5877454F5CC45A" authority="" authorityName="" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Hovamicrodon" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hovamicrodon silvester" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="silvester">Hovamicrodon silvester</taxonomicName>
Keiser, 1971: 251, by original designation. stat. n.
</paragraph>
